# TSStart

An opnionated tanstack-start app template for create-tsstart.

## What's included

- Runtime/Package Manager: bun
- Client: React + Vite
- Server: Vinxi
- RPC: tRPC
- DB: Drizzle + Libsql
- Auth: Lucia
- Route: Tanstack-Router
- Async: Tanstack-Query
- Table: Tanstack-Table + Shadcn
- State: Valtio
- Form: React-hook-form + zod
- UI: Shadcn + Tailwindcss
- Lint/Format: Eslint + Prettier
- Toast: Sonner
- Env: t3-oss/env-core

## Acknowledgements

- [tss-app - tsstart is mostly based on this project with some personal changes](https://github.com/ally-ahmed/tss-app)

## Getting Started

Clone project

## ENV

To run this project, you will need to add the following environment variables to your .env file

`GITHUB_CLIENT_ID=""`

`GITHUB_CLIENT_SECRET=""`

```bash
  git clone git@github.com:ally-ahmed/tss-app.git
  cd tss-app
```

Install depndencies

```bash
pnpm install
```

Create db and tables

```bash
pnpm db:push
```

Run app

```bash
pnpm dev
```
